3. python qmboxsize.py -i frame.pdb -s "((resid 723 and not name C O N H HA CA) or resid 729 or (resid 730 and name O1B O2B O3B O1A O2A O3A O5' C5' H9 H10 PB PA) or (resid 528 and not name C O N H HA CA CB CG HB2 HB3 HG2 HG3)) and not (resname WAT or type 'Na+' 'Cl-')"

